Reasoning: The paper discusses the importance of evidence from mobile phones in criminal investigations and the increasing need to investigate memory cards separately. This suggests that the paper is related to computer security (cs.CR) and data management (cs.DC). The development of a new tool also implies software engineering (cs.SE) and database systems (cs.DB). Finally, the testing of the tool with the WhatsApp application suggests a possible connection to cybercrime (cs.CY).
